1549	/**
1550	 * Debounced materialized view refresh coordinator.
1551	 *
1552	 * - mv_action_scores refresh: fast debounce (default 500ms) for SDK decision freshness.
1553	 * - mv_task_action_performance refresh: slower debounce (default 15s in production)
1554	 *   for dashboard/task aggregation workloads.
1555	 *
1556	 * ⚠️  NEVER AWAIT THIS FUNCTION.
1557	 * The returned Promise resolves when both debounce timers fire. Awaiting can
1558	 * stall the HTTP response and must be avoided in request handlers.
1559	 *
1560	 * Always call as fire-and-forget:
1561	 *   refreshTaskAggregation(customerId).catch(() => {});
1562	 *
1563	 * SIGTERM behaviour: timers in _taskPerfRefreshTimers / _actionScoresRefreshTimers are lost if the process
1564	 * exits during a debounce window. This is acceptable — mv_task_action_performance
1565	 * is eventually consistent and will self-heal on the next outcome log.
1566	 * decision-writer.ts has a SIGTERM flush for decisions (which are durable);
1567	 * MV refreshes deliberately do not, since they are idempotent and cheap.
